heading_10 = heading_5 + ">>Criminal Code Amendment Act 1913, containing the said further amendments And whereas the Acts and the parts of an Act which it is desirable to repeal are set out in the Appendix A and the compiled Act set out in Appendix B is a true compilation of the Acts and parts of Acts so directed to be compiled or authorised to be included in the compilation as aforesaid, and it is desirable to give such compilation the force of law. Be it therefore enacted by the Kings Most Excellent Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Legislative Council and Legislative Assembly of Western Australia, in this present Parliament assembled, and by the authority of the same, as follows"
