CONTEXT(heading_25, 'Threatens to do any injury, or cause any detriment of any kind to another with intent to prevent or hinder that other person from giving evidence before either House of Parliament, or before a committee of either House, or before a joint committee of both Houses or')
heading_26 = heading_24 + ">>(2) Threatens, or in any way punishes, damnifies, or injures, or attempts to punish, damnify, or injure any other person for having given such evidence, or on account of the evidence which he has given, unless such evidence was given in bad faith"
CONTEXT(heading_26, 'is guilty of a crime, and is liable, on conviction, to imprisonment for 5 years.')
